--- temp/linux-2.6.10-rc2/include/asm-x86_64/kprobes.h	2004-11-19 10:14:44.000000000 +0530
+++ linux-2.6.10-rc2/include/asm-x86_64/kprobes.h	2004-11-19 10:05:16.000000000 +0530
